title: Big Spenders, Bargain Buys, and Contrarian Picks | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck categorize their favorite and not-so-favorite daily fantasy players heading into Week 3, including go big or go home picks, buy lows of the week, bargain buys, and contrarian picks.
